.TH REVIEW_ARTIST_IDENTITY 1 "2026-03-18" "stophammer" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
review_artist_identity \- inspect duplicate artist-name groups and merge evidence
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B review_artist_identity
[
.BI --db " PATH"
] [
.BI --limit " N"
] [
.BI --name " NAME"
] [
.BI --feed-guid " GUID"
] [
.B --pending-feeds
] [
.B --json
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B review_artist_identity
reports duplicate lowercased artist-name groups and the staged evidence behind
each candidate so merge decisions can be reviewed safely.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI --db " PATH"
Path to the SQLite database. Defaults to
.BR ./stophammer.db .
.TP
.BI --limit " N"
Maximum number of duplicate-name groups to report. Defaults to 20.
.TP
.BI --name " NAME"
Restrict output to one lowercased artist-name key.
.TP
.BI --feed-guid " GUID"
Inspect the feed-scoped artist identity plan for one feed, including seed
artists and candidate merge groups considered by the targeted resolver.
.TP
.B --pending-feeds
List feeds whose targeted artist identity plan still contains candidate groups
to review.
.TP
.B --json
Emit machine-readable JSON instead of text output.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Review the top 20 duplicate-name groups:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_artist_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db --limit 20
.fi
.TP
Inspect one name as JSON:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_artist_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db --name mooky --json
.fi
.TP
Inspect one feed's targeted resolver plan:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_artist_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db --feed-guid feed-focus-b
.fi
.TP
List pending feeds with unresolved candidate groups:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_artist_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db --pending-feeds --limit 20
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR stophammer (1),
.BR backfill_canonical (1),
.BR backfill_artist_identity (1)
